inference. DUCOG (Dubrovnik Conference on Cognitive Science), 10th edition,
Dubrovnik, May 24-27.

(in press) I. Lorge and N. Katsos. Listener-adapted-speech: bilinguals adapt in a more
sensitive way,Linguistic Approaches to Bilingualism.

